get.description:
获取支持的市场列表

Returns:
    {
        "success": true,
        "data": {
            "markets": [
                {
                    "code": "CN",
                    "name": "A股",
                    "name_en": "China A-Shares",
                    "currency": "CNY",
                    "timezone": "Asia/Shanghai"
                },
                ...
            ]
        }
    }

搜索股票（支持多市场）

Args:
    market: 市场类型 (CN/HK/US)
    q: 搜索关键词
    limit: 返回结果数量

Returns:
    {
        "success": true,
        "data": {
            "stocks": [
                {
                    "code": "00700",
                    "name": "腾讯控股",
                    "name_en": "Tencent Holdings",
                    "market": "HK",
                    "source": "yfinance",
                    ...
                }
            ],
            "total": 1
        }
    }
